OL,3,CThree people arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after body found in wheelie bin
OL,6,FTwo men and a woman have been arrested
OL,7,Fon suspicion of murder after a man's
OL,8,Fbody was found in a wheelie bin in a
OL,9,Fpark in Coventry.
OL,11,FPolice said the body of the man, who
OL,12,Fhas not yet been identified but who is
OL,13,Fbelieved to be aged 40 to 50, was
OL,14,Ffound in Cash's Park off Daimler Road
OL,15,Fat around 5.00pm on Friday 13 March.
OL,17,FThree people, a woman in her 40s, a
OL,18,Fman in his 40s and a man in his 20s,
OL,19,Fwere arrested overnight in Blackpool
OL,20,Fon suspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
