OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773667689
OL,3,CThree people arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after body found in wheelie bin
OL,6,FPolice are working with the local
OL,7,Fauthority to identify the location of
OL,8,Fthe Coventry City Council wheelie bin
OL,9,Fbefore it was moved.
OL,11,FIt's believed the man may have been
OL,12,Fhit by a vehicle before being moved to
OL,13,FCash's Park.
OL,15,FPolice are carrying out urgent
OL,16,Fenquiries to establish who the man is
OL,17,Fand where and how he died.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
