OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1773667689
OL,3,CThree people arrested on suspicion of
OL,4,Cmurder after body found in wheelie bin
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Phil Poole
OL,7,Ffrom our Major Crime Unit said: "After
OL,8,Fbeginning our investigation this
OL,9,Fweekend, we have made a number of
OL,10,Farrests overnight.
OL,12,F"All of these people remain in custody
OL,13,Fat this time while we continue to
OL,14,Fbuild a picture of what might have
OL,15,Fhappened.
OL,17,F"Thank you to everyone who has been in
OL,18,Ftouch providing information so far.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
